===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally written as {{och-l|*从}}. Now {{Han compound|辵|从|t1=walk|t2=follow|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|nocap=y}}.

===Etymology 1===
Etymology not certain. Perhaps cognate with {{cog|bo|རྫོང་བ||to dispatch; to dismiss}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Alternatively, compare {{cog|bo|སྟོངས་པ||to accompany}}, or perhaps {{och-l|送|to escort; to send}}.

Pronunciation 2 is a derivation of pronunciation 1.

